            <span class="highlight">Mandatory</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cui-rule error">
            <span class="cui-ref">D+Tc-0019</span>
            <a href="http://www.mscui.net/DesignGuide/QuickGuides/DateTimeInput/Date/CalInput/keyboard.aspx">Ensure that the control can be operated effectively via the keyboard (for example, using arrow keys)</a>
            <span class="highlight">Mandatory</span>
            <span class="rule-not-met">HTML5 support may vary by browser. Inappropriate for touch interfaces</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cui-rule error">
            <span class="cui-ref">D+Tc-0011</span>
            <a href="http://www.mscui.net/DesignGuide/QuickGuides/DateTimeInput/Date/CalInput/editing.aspx">Provide the ability to select a month independently, and a year independently. Signify the interactivity of these elements by suitable styling, for example as buttons or links, and ensure that they have descriptive tooltips</a>
