        <div class="cui-rule error">
            <span class="cui-ref">D+Tc-0025</span>
            <a href="http://www.mscui.net/DesignGuide/QuickGuides/DateTimeInput/Time/arithmetic.aspx">Allow users to enter arithmetic shortcuts such as '+3h' for three hours later and '-2m' for two minutes earlier. The relevant operators are as illustrated</a>
